# proof_debt: prove colored flag sequences are labeled flag permutations modulo same-color permutations.

(9 * 8 * 7 * 6 * 5 * 4 * 3 * 2 * 1) / ((4 * 3 * 2 * 1) * (3 * 2 * 1) * (2 * 1)) = 1260
